title: MacPhail progressing in search for Phils GM (Los Angeles Angels of Anaheim)
text: ( Source : Los Angeles Angels of Anaheim ) It is likely MacPhail has interviewed others. MLB .com identified Klentak in June as a favorite to replace former general manager Ruben Amaro Jr. , when reports first surfaced about MacPhail's arrival.
